page.title: Home
page.content: This is an example page. It’s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

description.pl: Frontend Developer z 3 letnim doświadczeniem w projektach komercyjnych, głównie w branży e-commerce. Tworzę skalowalne aplikacje webowe z wykorzystaniem React, TypeScript i Node.js, integruję systemy oraz automatyzuję procesy biznesowe z użyciem narzędzi takich jak AWS Lambda, n8n i Make.
description.en: Frontend Developer with 3 years of experience in commercial projects, mainly in the e-commerce industry. Development of scalable web applications using React, TypeScript and Node.js, integration of systems and automation of business processes using tools such as AWS Lambda, n8n and Make.
